<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The price of this item has been increased to 3000, up from 2880.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 30 (May 27th, 2014)</h4>Fixed a bug where the attack speed reduction component of this item's passive was applying to structures.<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28 (April 8, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the attack speed slow was incorrectly flagged as a movement speed slow, subsequently causing it to be reduced in duration by disable reduction effects.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The Unique Passive: Wither has been reworked and renamed to Subdue.</li><li>Unique Passive: Subdue - Dealing damage will reduce the target's Power by 10 and attack speed by 30% for 3 seconds.</li><li>Price increased to 2880, up from 2560.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 15 (October 22, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing this item's passive ability not to work in certain circumstances.</li></ul>